linux ubuntu 16.04下deb文件的安装以及一些问题的解决:
https://blog.csdn.net/FontThrone/article/details/78066308

sudo apt-get install cmake libgtest-dev
cd /usr/src/gtest
sudo cmake CMakeLists.txt
sudo make
 
# copy or symlink libgtest.a and libgtest_main.a to your /usr/lib folder
sudo cp *.a /usr/lib

json错误解决方法：
fatal error: json/json.h: No such file or directory #265
Symlinking /usr/include/jsoncpp/json to /usr/include/json does help.

